0},"children":["We become your remote ",["$","em",null,{"children":"operations department."}]]}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Hired Billing Support gives multi-location groups a standardized, embedded operations layer that runs the work consistently across every site — at a fraction of the cost of doing it in-house. Same SOPs everywhere. Same KPIs. Same accountability."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"You'll have a dedicated operations lead from our side who functions as a department head — reporting into your COO, owning the operational scorecard across all sites, and managing the team that executes underneath them."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Your office managers stop fighting fires and start managing patient experience. Your billing director stops chasing eleven workflows and starts running one. Your COO stops recruiting and starts strategizing."}],["$","p",null,{"style":{"fontFamily":"var(--serif)","fontStyle":"italic","fontSize":22,"color":"var(--paper)","marginTop":32,"maxWidth":700},"children":"The chaos doesn't disappear because you wished it away. It disappears because someone is finally running it as one operation."}]]}]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"block warm","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"block-head fade-in","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"eyebrow","children":"What we run for enterprise groups"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"display","children":["The full operational ",["$","em",null,{"children":"stack — standardized."}]]}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Every capability built to run across multiple sites, multiple EHRs, and multiple specialties from a single accountable layer."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"svc-grid-2 fade-in","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"svc-card","children":[["$","h4",null,{"children":"Centralized RCM"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"One billing operation across every site. Same SOPs, same QA standards, same KPIs. Site-level reporting, group-lev